%script{src: 'https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.3.1.min.js'}
%script{src: '/js/quick.js'}

%p{id: 'step1'}
  How much are you going to invest:
  %input{type: 'number', id: 'btc', oninput: 'wts_recalc();', style: 'width:5em', autocomplete: 'off', required: true, tabindex: 1, autofocus: true, value: '0.1'}
  BTC
  (you will get
  %span{id: 'zld'}
  ZLD)
  %br
  For how long you will hodl:
  %input{type: 'number', id: 'months', oninput: 'wts_recalc();', style: 'width:3em', autocomplete: 'off', required: true, tabindex: 2, value: '6'}
  months
  %br
  You will spend
  %span{id: 'spend'}
  USD now and will get
  %span{id: 'back'}
  USD back;
  your profit will be
  %span{id: 'profit'}
  USD.

%p{id: 'step2', style: 'display: none'}
  Your mobile phone:
  %input{type: 'text', name: 'phone', id: 'phone', pattern: "[0-9]+", size: 17, placeholder: 'e.g. 14085551234', required: true, tabindex: 4}
  %span.small.gray{id: 'step2-help'}
    A text message will be sent with an authorization code.

%p{id: 'step3', style: 'display: none'}
  4-digit authorization code:
  %input{type: 'text', name: 'code', id: 'code', pattern: "[0-9]+", size: 5, autocomplete: 'off', tabindex: 5}
  %span.small.gray{id: 'step3-help'}
    Find it in the text message delivered to your phone.

%p{id: 'step4', style: 'display: none'}
  This is your
  = succeed ':' do
    %a{href: 'https://blog.zold.io/2018/07/18/keygap.html'} keygap
  = succeed '.' do
    %code{id: 'keygap'}
  Write it down where it's safe.
  If you lose it, you will lose your Zold coins!
  We will not be able to restore this information!

%p{id: 'step5', style: 'display: none'}
  %img{id: 'qr', style: 'float:right;margin-left:.5em;margin-bottom:.5em;width:128px;height:128px;', src: ''}
  Send
  %strong
    %span{id: 'amount'}
    bitcoins
  to this address:
  %code{id: 'address'}
  Once the payment arrives (may take up to 30 minutes), you can go to
  %a{href: '/mobile_send'} your account
  where you will be able to manage your wallet, convert ZLD back to bitcoins
  and send payments to other users.
  Thanks for joining Zold community and helping Zerocracy
  make the world of software development better!

%p{id: 'step6'}
  %input{type: 'submit', id: 'button', tabindex: 5, value: 'Start'}
  %br
  %span.small.gray{id: 'error'}
    To start over just reload the page.

